36
00:02:02,421 --> 00:02:04,182
Yeah, Young Lord.

37
00:02:04,462 --> 00:02:06,501
You hold grudges against
Chun Keling, don't you?

38
00:02:07,022 --> 00:02:09,581
I helped you to avenge with the fire.

39
00:02:10,382 --> 00:02:13,502
