42
00:02:18,861 --> 00:02:20,901
I indeed lit the fire.

43
00:02:22,021 --> 00:02:23,782
But it's the rainy season recently.

44
00:02:23,942 --> 00:02:27,021
It's quite damp,
so the fire might not catch on.

45
00:02:27,141 --> 00:02:29,181
You could understand, right?

46
